§390.2. Shreveport railroad crossings; remediation or removal
A. Railroad companies shall remediate or remove any existing blighted or
abandoned railroads and associated structures in the city of Shreveport, parish of
Caddo, not later than January 1, 2027.
B. Underpasses of railroad crossings within the city of Shreveport shall be
maintained and preserved, including but not limited to painting and rust removal, to
prevent them from becoming a blight or nuisance.
